Theorem Lookup-store-weakening-H: forall env, forall env', forall l, forall t, {subsetEnvH env env'} -> {lookupEnvH env l t} -> {lookupEnvH env' l t}. 
IH0 : induction on 1. intros Main Lookup. Subset: case Main.  
 search.  
 apply IH0 to Subset Lookup.  
 search. 


